  "body": "<!--\r\nNeed help?\r\nRefer to our contributing guidelines for additional information about making a good issue:\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/.github/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nThe `Proxy_EOA` contract uses a non standard storage slot to hold the address of the implementation address. [EIP-1967](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1967) defines a standard storage slot to use for proxies. We should adopt the standard.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/pull/545#discussion_r617955845",
